      <description lang="en">The An-Nahar Lebanon Newspaper Text Corpus comprises articles in standard Arabic from 1995 to 2000 (6 years) stored as HTML files on CDRom media. Each year contains 45 000 articles and 24 million words. Each article includes information such as title, newspaper's name, date, country, type, page, etc. For each year, the size in byte is as follows:1995 :	128 MB1996 :	138 MB1997 :	152 MB1998 :	140 MB1999 :	130 MB2000 :	118 MB</description>
